      "body" : "This is generally correct, but beware of its limits.  If you do <code>double rangeMax= Double.MAX_VALUE;</code> and <code>double rangeMin= -rangeMax;</code> you will always get an infinite value in return.  You might want to check for <code>Double.valueOf(rangeMax-rangeMin).isInfinite()</code>."
