    "body" : "<p>To generate a random value between <code>rangeMin</code> and <code>rangeMax</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Random r = new Random();\ndouble randomValue = rangeMin + (rangeMax - rangeMin) * r.nextDouble();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 178949,
      "reputation" : 12429,
      "user_id" : 411247,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 91,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/of4bM.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Topera",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/411247/topera"
    },
