  "title" : "Generate a random double in a range",
  "body" : "<p>I have two doubles like the following</p>\n\n<pre><code>double min = 100;\ndouble max = 101;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and with a random generator, I need to create a double value between the range of min and max.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Random r = new Random();\nr.nextDouble();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>but there is nothing here where we can specify the range.</p>\n"
